title: Naft Omidiyeh F.C.
text:
Naft Omidiyeh Football Club is an Iranian <a href="Football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club based in <a href="Omidiyeh">Omidiyeh</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. They currently compete in the <a href="2016%E2%80%9317%20Iran%20Football%27s%202nd%20Division">2016–17 Iran Football's 2nd Division</a>.
